Hi Sch=C3=B6neicher,

You'll find the latest sources on these two git repos:

ddccontrol.git.sourceforge.net/gitroot/ddccontrol/ddccontrol
ddccontrol.git.sourceforge.net/gitroot/ddccontrol/ddccontrol-db

To make it work, you need to make an XML file of you monitor data called
LP2475W.xml. Use HWP2647.xml as a template, for instance. And look to
other monitor files for examples of enhanced features.

If you are able to make most functions work, please send us the XML
file, and we'll add it to the source code.

--=20
Regards,
Lars Tobias


